{
  "stem": "3638.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A few times.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he caught me one day sleeping.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the same, the same as with this policeman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He caught me one day sleeping on the job, and so he also, he warned me that, if he catch me again, I'll lose the job.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's all he did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He didn't, he didn't, he did not do me anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a tall fellow, not bad looking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say he would be in his 50s, 40, 45.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wouldn't be more.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the time smoking, always cigarette in his hand.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was a chain smoker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nicely dressed, with perfume all over his place, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's how he was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he used to-- when he went on the inspection, he always talk to the Polish foreman.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He always talk to the Polish foreman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, when, when they work at nighttime, they had an idea.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As soon as the car drive, drove-- because the, the gate wasn't very far from the main factory.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The factory was on the right-hand side, and the gate was out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So as soon as they hear gate, they knew Schindler's coming, because they start to, you know, to make, make themselves busy, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Poles were there before we came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only the Poles.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were quite nice people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were not, they were not bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The foreman, as long as you did the job, they knew that we are here because of this business.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they treat us-- as long as you have, you have, you have to do the job.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if, if you did the job, they didn't do you any harm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They still went-- the Poles always went home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't know whether they work on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
